Top Arrows: Change Hat
Middle Arrows: Change Shirt
Bottom Arrows: Change Pants
Color Picker: Change Head Color


Load Textbox:

Use the load textbox to load a specific
outfit. The number in the textbox
will change as you customize, copy it
if you would like to load your current
outfit later, then press the \"Load\"
button to load it."
